        <h4>Make sure ethdo checksum matches</h4>
<pre><code>shasum -a 256 ethdo-1.36.1-darwin-amd64.tar.gz
cat ethdo-1.36.1-darwin-amd64.tar.gz.sha256</code></pre>
        <p>Both of these output values should have matching checksum. If they do not match, there might be a security issue and you should seek further support.</p>
        <h4>Extract the ethdo archive</h4>
        <pre><code>tar xvf ethdo-1.36.1-darwin-amd64.tar.gz</code></pre>
